{"article_id":"v5NM6bI37DqDyUbU","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Republican Rep. Darrell Issa declared Thursday","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"that the embattled IRS official","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"who refused to testify Wednesday","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"had no right","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"to do so ,","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"and is now looking to haul her back before his committee .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"The chairman of the House oversight committee made the call","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"after consulting with attorneys about IRS official Lois Lerner 's bizarre appearance before the panel on Wednesday .","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"Lerner , the head of the exempt organizations division","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"which oversaw the controversial targeting of conservative groups ,","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"caused confusion Wednesday morning","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"when she pleaded the Fifth","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"and refused to answer questions","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"-- but also delivered an opening statement","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"in which she asserted her innocence .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"Though Issa dismissed her from the hearing room ,","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"he questioned at the time","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"whether she had waived her rights","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"by delivering the statement .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"A spokesman told Fox News on Thursday","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"that Issa had reached a decision .","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"`` After consulting with counsel ,","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"Chairman Issa has concluded","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"that Ms. Lerner 's 5th amendment assertion is no longer valid , ''","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"spokesman Ali Ahmad said .","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"`` She remains under subpoena ,","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"the Committee is looking at recalling her for testimony . ''","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"Issa ,","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"citing the concerns over Lerner 's comments ,","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"never actually adjourned the hearing","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"--","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"where other current and former Treasury and IRS officials testified .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"He only called it into recess .","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"The thinking among Republicans is that they can still call her back to testify .","depth":4},{"id":34,"text":"More On This ...","depth":3},{"id":35,"text":"IRS official on leave refused to resign ,","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"GOP senator says","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"Issa told Fox News on Thursday","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"that she ca n't put the genie `` back in the bottle . '' Republicans are accusing Lerner of trying to have it both ways .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"`` If you could do it the way","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"she wants to do it ,","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"then every defendant would come ,","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"say","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"' I did n't rob the bank ,","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"and I 'm not going to answer the prosecutor 's questions , ' ''","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"Rep. Trey Gowdy , R-S.C. , told Fox News .","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"`` So we 'd all in life like to get out our version","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"without having to answer anyone else 's questions .","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"It 's just not fair .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"And I do n't think","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"it 's legal . ''","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"`` I have not done anything wrong , ''","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"she said .","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"`` I have not broken any laws .","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"I have not violated any IRS rules or regulations ,","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"and I have not provided false information to this or any other congressional committee . ''","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"Lerner is represented by lawyer William W. Taylor ,","depth":5},{"id":57,"text":"who is noted for winning a dismissal of all charges against former IMF director Dominique Strauss-Kahn in a high-profile sexual assault case .","depth":5},{"id":58,"text":"It 's unclear whether Lerner can avoid another round of questioning by the committee .","depth":4},{"id":59,"text":"Rep. Elijah Cummings , D-Md. , the top Democrat on the committee","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"who was as tough as any Republican on the IRS witnesses Wednesday ,","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"he thought","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"Lerner was still in her right","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"to refuse to answer questions .","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"`` I 'd like to see","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"( hearings )","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"run like a federal court .","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"Unfortunately , this is not a federal court","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"and she does have a right , ''","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"Cummings said Wednesday .","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"`` And we have to adhere to that . ''","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"A brief assessment by the Cato Institute agreed ,","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"that unlike in a courtroom , Lerner could in a hearing room `` selectively '' invoke her Fifth Amendment right .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"Former IRS Commissioner Doug Shulman ,","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"who stayed","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"to testify Wednesday ,","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"endured a tough round of questioning for the second day in a row .","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"Lawmakers were visibly frustrated","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"as he struggled to explain","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"why he did n't notify Congress","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"after learning of the practice last year .","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"But lawmakers are itching to question Lerner ,","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"having aired a string of complaints about her own failure","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"to notify Congress .","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"Lerner touched off the public controversy","depth":5},{"id":87,"text":"when , at an American Bar Association conference this month , she apologized for the IRS ' practice","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"of targeting conservative organizations for additional scrutiny .","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"It was the first time","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"the agency acknowledged the practice .","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"She said","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"she had n't revealed the information sooner ,","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"because she was never asked .","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"But just two days before the ABA conference , Lerner was specifically asked about the investigation .","depth":6},{"id":95,"text":"Rep. Joseph Crowley , D-N.Y. ,","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"who had asked her about it ,","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"later called her answer evasive .","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"`` The bottom line is you can not lie to Congress ,","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"and you can not be evasive ,","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"you can not try to mislead Congress , ''","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"he said .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":203,"left":135,"right":202,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":135,"left":120,"right":134,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":109,"right":119,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":107,"right":108,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":107,"left":0,"right":106,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":106,"left":105,"right":5,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":105,"left":103,"right":104,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":103,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":108,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"}